content.body:
### Shop 9.5 x 16.5 Tire Size
The 9.5 x 16.5 tire size is a specialty size that you might find on commercial vehicles, trailers, and some older pickup trucks. If you’re looking for a set of 9.5 x 16.5 tires, chances are you need dependable traction, long wear, and a tough construction that can hold up to rough use. 

If you’re looking for a new 9.5 x 16.5 tire then take a look at the [Power King Super Highway II](https://simpletire.com/brands/power-king-tires/super-highway-ii), Tyre Advance Super Tracker Plus XL, and Specialty Tires of America STA Super Traxion Tread A, as each tire is more than capable of performing and withstanding demanding use.

Maybe you're looking for 9.50-16.5 trailer tires. If that's the case, take a look at the [Deestone D902](https://simpletire.com/brands/deestone-tires/d902), Galaxy Trailer Special, and Greenball Tow-Master Hiway Rib.

Whether you need a commercial, trailer, or another type of tire, SimpleTire has a set of 9.5x 16.5 tires that meets your needs at a great price!
